msgid ""
"This is a simple configuration intended to run on EC2 with S3 permanent "
"storage. Values for the default setting can be changed simply by editing "
"this file, uncommenting the relevant lines and adding your own settings. All"
" you need to do to get this configuration to work is to either set the "
